  <h1 class="gd-h1">Heliskiing in British Columbia</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">British Columbia is the birthplace of commercial heliskiing and still the benchmark for the sport, famous for deep dry powder, vast interior ranges and comfortable lodge-based weeks from December to April. This guide covers everything you need before you look at <a href="/packages">the packages</a> or consider spring skiing in <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
